Note on the BioDIV (e120) dataset:

The aboveground-biomass CSV optionally fetched by `download_data.py` is NOT
distributed with this repository. It is hosted by the Environmental Data
Initiative under

  Tilman, D. "Plant Aboveground Biomass Data" (knb-lter-cdr.273.11)
  https://doi.org/10.6073/pasta/27ddb5d8aebe24db99caa3933e9bc8e2

and is licensed CC BY 4.0. Any use of the downloaded CSV must cite the
original dataset and the Isbell et al. (Nature, 2026) study from which the
perturbation/recovery convention is adopted.
